TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Ammon Center Married Women's volleyball team, from left, kneeling: two unknown women, Mrs. George, and Irene Robinson; standing: Mildred Allen, Ruth Lucas, Rosa Lee, Nettie Myers, Delores Hill, Vonnie Hill, Beatrice McHaffey, Carleen Coleman, and Pauline Penex, posed in interior, possilby Ammon Center
